  2568                                  ;       Console Task
  2569                                  ;
  2570                                  ;       The only task defined in the kernel is the console task. This task consists of code, data, stack, and task state
  2571                                  ;       segments and a local descriptor table. The console task accepts and echos user keyboard input to the console
  2572                                  ;       screen and responds to user commands.
