  2652                                  ;       Console Code                                                            @disk: 008600   @mem: 005000
  2653                                  ;
  2654                                  ;       This is the code for the console task. The task is defined in the GDT in two descriptors, the Local Descriptor
  2655                                  ;       Table (LDT) at 0050h and the Task State Segment (TSS) at 0058h. Jumping to or calling a TSS selector causes a
  2656                                  ;       task switch, giving control to the code for the task at the CS:IP defined in the TSS for the current ring level.
  2657                                  ;       The initial CS:IP in the Console TSS is 24h:0, where 24h is a selector in the LDT. This selector points to the
  2658                                  ;       concode section, loaded into memory 5000h by the Loader. The console task is dedicated to accepting user key-
  2659                                  ;       board input, echoing to the console screen and responding to user commands.
  2660                                  ;
  2661                                  ;       When control reaches this section, our addressability is set up according to the following diagram.
  2662                                  ;
  2663                                  ;       DS,ES --------> 000000  +-----------------------------------------------+ DS,ES:0000
  2664                                  ;                               |  Real Mode Interrupt Vectors                  |
  2665                                  ;                       000400  +-----------------------------------------------+ DS,ES:0400
  2666                                  ;                               |  Reserved BIOS Memory Area                    |
  2667                                  ;                       000800  +-----------------------------------------------+ DS,ES:0800
  2668                                  ;                               |  Shared Kernel Memory Area                    |
  2669                                  ;                       001000  +-----------------------------------------------+               <-- GDTR
  2670                                  ;                               |  Global Descriptor Table (GDT)                |
  2671                                  ;                       001800  +-----------------------------------------------+               <-- IDTR
  2672                                  ;                               |  Interrupt Descriptor Table (IDT)             |
  2673                                  ;                       002000  +-----------------------------------------------+
  2674                                  ;                               |  Interrupt Handlers                           |
  2675                                  ;                               |  Kernel Function Library                      |
  2676                                  ;       SS -----------> 004000  +===============================================+ SS:0000
  2677                                  ;                               |  Console Task Stack Area                      |
  2678                                  ;       SS:SP --------> 004700  +-----------------------------------------------+ SS:0700       <-- LDTR = GDT.SEL 0050h
  2679                                  ;                               |  Console Task Local Descriptor Table (LDT)    |
  2680                                  ;                       004780  +-----------------------------------------------+               <-- TR  = GDT.SEL 0058h
  2681                                  ;                               |  Console Task Task State Segment (TSS)        |
  2682                                  ;                       004800  +-----------------------------------------------+
  2683                                  ;                               |  Console Task Message Queue                   |
  2684                                  ;       CS,CS:IP -----> 005000  +-----------------------------------------------+ CS:0000
  2685                                  ;                               |  Console Task Code                            |
  2686                                  ;                               |  Console Task Constants                       |
  2687                                  ;                       006000  +===============================================+
